high_descs: Turn and go to the toilet roll holder by the toilet.
Pick up the toilet roll off of the toilet roll holder.
Turn and go to the sink.
Put the toilet roll in the cabinet under the sink.
Turn and go to the bathtub.
Pick up the toilet roll on the bathtub.
Turn and go to the sink.
Put the toilet roll in the cabinet under the sink.
anns.task_desc: Move two toilet rolls to the cabinet under the sink.

high_descs: Go to the toilet roll
Pick up the toilet roll
Go to the sink cabinet
Put the toilet roll in the sink cabinet
Go to the tub
Pick up the empty toilet roll
Go to the sink cabinet
Put the empty toilet roll in the sink cabinet

high_descs: Go to the toilet paper holder on the left side of the toilet.
Pick up the toilet paper from the holder.
Turn around and go to the right cabinet below the sink.
Place the toilet paper inside the cabinet.
Turn left and go to the right side of the bath tub.
Pick up the empty toilet paper roll on the right side of the tub.
Turn left and go back to the cabinet below the sink.
Place the empty toilet paper roll on the right of the new toilet paper roll.
anns.task_desc: Move the toilet paper rolls to the cabinet below the sink.
